<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/usc/t2/s105">Section 105 of Title 2</ref>, referred to in text, was editorially reclassified as <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s4303">section 4303 of Title 2</ref>, The Congress.</p>
</note>
